<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.5.4">
<l>mēle ḻuntatōr vāyuki ḷarntu</l>
<l rend="indent">mēlmi ṭaṟṟiṉai yuḷḷeḻa vāṅki</l>
<l>kāluṅ kaiyumvi tirvitirt tēṟik</l>
<l rend="indent">kaṇṇu ṟakkama tāvataṉ muṉṉam</l>
<l>mūla mākiya voṟṟaiye ḻuttai</l>
<l rend="indent">mūṉṟu māttirai yuḷḷeḻa vāṅki</l>
<l>vēlai vaṇṇaṉai mēvuti rākil</l>
<l rend="indent">viṇṇa kattiṉil mēvalu māmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before the last rising breath is expelled,</l>
<l rend="indent">the windpipe ceases to function,</l>
<l rend="indent">the arms and legs are possessed</l>
<l rend="indent">by trembling and shaking,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the eyes sleep [forever]-</l>
<l>before that happens,</l>
<l>take in the three measures of the one letter</l>
<l rend="indent">that is the Cause so that [your] heart swells,</l>
<l>if you love the sea-hued Lord,</l>
<l rend="indent">[your] dwelling place will be in heaven.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
